title: The Power Of The Blessing | Joel Osteen

description:
There is a blessing over your life that gives you a supernatural advantage. Because you are God's anointed, He is going before you to arrange things in your favor. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
